- [siren blaring]
- [horn honks]

171
00:06:49,050 --> 00:06:52,082
[Frank] <i>Anybody else like to
offer a different interpretation?</i>

172
00:06:52,084 --> 00:06:53,582
[Lieberman] <i>None of this
can be proved.</i>

173
00:06:53,584 --> 00:06:55,015
