knows all of this?

180
00:07:02,850 --> 00:07:04,148
[Frank] No.

181
00:07:04,150 --> 00:07:05,682
<i>Or you'd already
be eating shit.</i>

182
00:07:05,684 --> 00:07:07,482
<i>It'd have been in the paper
the next day.</i>

183
00:07:07,484 --> 00:07:09,215
[Lieberman] <i>The girl,
she married? Got family?</i>

184
00:07:09,217 --> 00:07:10,649
[Frank] <i>It's all in my file.</i>

185
00:07:10,651 --> 00:07:12,382
<i>Her mother's dead.
No brother or sisters.</i>

186
00:07:12,384 --> 00:07:14,582
