212
00:08:31,175 --> 00:08:32,507
- <i>Just assessing value...</i>
- [Lou] <i>You can forget it!</i>

213
00:08:32,509 --> 00:08:34,140
Jeez, Lou.

214
00:08:34,142 --> 00:08:36,207
What is your beef with a guy
gettin' paid for good work?

215
00:08:36,209 --> 00:08:37,707
As far as I can see,
you get paid

216
00:08:37,709 --> 00:08:39,507
