- [groans]

217
00:08:39,509 --> 00:08:40,906
- [Giant Man] <i>Watch your mouth.</i>
- [Frank] <i>Jesus, take it easy.</i>

218
00:08:40,908 --> 00:08:42,107
- Shit.
