- [Lou] What the fuck?

222
00:08:46,609 --> 00:08:48,140
Listen, motherfucker,
I'm gonna have my friend

223
00:08:48,142 --> 00:08:49,507
<i>shove that right up your ass.</i>

224
00:08:49,509 --> 00:08:50,741
[Lieberman] <i>Enough.
Lou, a word.</i>

225
00:08:50,743 --> 00:08:53,173
[indistinct conversation]

226
00:08:53,175 --> 00:08:56,040
[Frank] Oh, come on, fellas,
don't get in a twist.

227
00:08:56,042 --> 00:08:57,340
It's just business.

228
