00:23:22,576 --> 00:23:24,109
[applause]

496
00:23:25,342 --> 00:23:27,806
Well, I'll be damned,
he did it.

497
00:23:27,808 --> 00:23:29,173
I told you.

498
00:23:29,175 --> 00:23:31,007
He's no pushover, this one.

499
00:23:31,009 --> 00:23:32,307
[Mayor] Ladies and gentlemen,

500
00:23:32,309 --> 00:23:34,309
