- Mr. Mayor! Mr. Mayor!
- [reporters clamoring]

504
00:23:43,542 --> 00:23:44,842
This way.

505
00:23:47,775 --> 00:23:49,309
[laughter]

506
00:23:50,676 --> 00:23:52,240
[Mayor] And after all that,

507
00:23:52,242 --> 00:23:54,540
he voted for the wrong guy
in three different precincts.

508
00:23:54,542 --> 00:23:56,507
[laughter]

509
00:23:56,509 --> 00:23:58,073
[Moses] What is this shit?

510
00:23:58,075 --> 00:24:00,173
What about City Planning?

511
00:24:00,175 --> 00:24:02,107
See here now, Mo.
What is all this?

512
00:24:02,109 --> 00:24:03,707
Don't you play games
with me, you fuckin' mutt.

513
00:24:03,709 --> 00:24:06,274
Either I get City Planning
or I quit the other two.

514
00:24:06,276 --> 00:24:07,307
Right now!

515
00:24:07,309 --> 00:24:09,140
The reporters are still here.

516
00:24:09,142 --> 00:24:11,940
Easy now, it's nothing
to get hot about.

517
00:24:11,942 --> 00:24:14,207
It's probably
just an oversight.

518
00:24:14,209 --> 00:24:15,806
They forgot to
give me the blank.

519
00:24:15,808 --> 00:24:17,741
Just give us a day
to get settled in,

520
00:24:17,743 --> 00:24:19,009
and I'll see to it.

521
00:24:35,975 --> 00:24:37,175
Now sign it.

522
00:24:46,509 --> 00:24:47,842
Now give me.

523
00:24:53,376 --> 00:24:54,641
Right.

524
00:24:54,643 --> 00:24:56,975
Bunch of fuckin' amateurs.

525
00:24:59,709 --> 00:25:02,374
- Close the damn door and keep it closed!
- [door slams]

526
00:25:02,376 --> 00:25:03,873
[announcer on radio]
<i>City sports authority</i>

527
00:25:03,875 --> 00:25:05,574
<i>reports new life
in negotiations</i>

528
00:25:05,576 --> 00:25:06,873
<i>with Walter O'Malley to keep
