his arm all fucked up?

1588
01:19:23,834 --> 01:19:26,065
- Mmm-mmm.
- Colored Marine Unit,

1589
01:19:26,067 --> 01:19:27,165
carryin' ammo,

1590
01:19:27,167 --> 01:19:28,732
and one day,
he picked up a gun

1591
01:19:28,734 --> 01:19:32,065
