suicide attack, got hit.

1592
01:19:32,067 --> 01:19:34,898
Came back from that war
bitter as hell.

1593
01:19:34,900 --> 01:19:37,201
Damn shame, too,
'cause he could play.

1594
01:19:38,101 --> 01:19:39,099
Trombone.

1595
01:19:39,101 --> 01:19:40,765
- Hmm.
