back in the '40s.

1597
01:19:44,301 --> 01:19:46,498
You ever met his wife?

1598
01:19:46,500 --> 01:19:47,965
Sarge ain't never married.

1599
01:19:47,967 --> 01:19:49,531
What about Laura's mother?

1600
01:19:49,533 --> 01:19:51,531
I don't know nothin'
about that.

1601
01:19:51,533 --> 01:19:53,432
It was just Laura and him.

1602
01:19:53,434 --> 01:19:55,199
She was a tiny little thing,

1603
01:19:55,201 --> 01:19:58,167
