readin' while we was playin'.

1604
01:19:59,434 --> 01:20:00,999
You play?

1605
01:20:01,001 --> 01:20:03,598
- Music? No.
- Now, I'm not so keen

1606
01:20:03,600 --> 01:20:06,101
