while we playin'...

1607
01:20:07,434 --> 01:20:09,466
but you was on the line.

1608
01:20:09,468 --> 01:20:10,865
I could hear it.

1609
01:20:10,867 --> 01:20:13,299
On the line, Lionel.
Lionel's on the line.

1610
01:20:13,301 --> 01:20:15,132
[sighs] Sorry, I...

1611
01:20:15,134 --> 01:20:18,132
I got somethin' wrong
with my head...

1612
01:20:18,134 --> 01:20:21,565
and the music really, really
set it off. I'm sorry.

1613
01:20:21,567 --> 01:20:22,965
Don't be sorry.

1614
01:20:22,967 --> 01:20:25,466
You got a head
just like mine,

1615
01:20:25,468 --> 01:20:28,132
always boilin' over.

1616
01:20:28,134 --> 01:20:29,934
Turnin' things around.

1617
01:20:31,134 --> 01:20:32,199
