more than you control it,

1619
01:20:34,401 --> 01:20:35,798
once it gets in you.

1620
01:20:35,800 --> 01:20:37,199
Some people call it a gift,

1621
01:20:37,201 --> 01:20:39,165
but it's a brain affliction
just the same.

1622
01:20:39,167 --> 01:20:41,099
Yeah, well,
I just twitch and shout.

1623
01:20:41,101 --> 01:20:43,531
At least you got a horn
to push it through,

1624
01:20:43,533 --> 01:20:45,332
make it sound pretty.

1625
01:20:45,334 --> 01:20:48,466
Yeah, but there's a lot of
other hours in the day, though.

1626
01:20:48,468 --> 01:20:50,232
You know what I'm sayin'?

1627
01:20:50,234 --> 01:20:51,700
Too many.

