1634
01:21:17,201 --> 01:21:19,199
- I know Jake Gleason.
- [stammers] Jake Gleason

1635
01:21:19,201 --> 01:21:20,999
took me to the Hamilton
hearing the other night.

1636
01:21:21,001 --> 01:21:22,765
- I heard you speak.
- Oh.

1637
01:21:22,767 --> 01:21:24,865
I'm a new writer
with the <i>Times.</i>

1638
01:21:24,867 --> 01:21:28,099
