to a friend of mine.

1959
01:35:23,001 --> 01:35:26,001
I'm sorry. I'm really sorry.

1960
01:35:27,134 --> 01:35:29,600
You got someone
that you can call?

1961
01:35:32,468 --> 01:35:33,867
