1965
01:35:57,401 --> 01:35:58,934
You want me to?

1966
01:36:13,533 --> 01:36:14,598
If!

1967
01:36:14,600 --> 01:36:16,399
Oh, God, I'm sorry.

1968
01:36:16,401 --> 01:36:17,600
- It's okay.
- Shit.

1969
01:36:19,067 --> 01:36:20,067
I'm...

1970
01:36:21,267 --> 01:36:22,631
I'm sorry. I...

1971
01:36:22,633 --> 01:36:23,898
