- It's okay.

1973
01:36:28,767 --> 01:36:30,567
Thank you for staying.

1974
01:36:31,967 --> 01:36:33,101
Yeah, sure.

1975
01:36:38,967 --> 01:36:41,067
I know how you're feelin'.
I really do.

1976
01:36:43,834 --> 01:36:47,232
Pretty soon, you're gonna hear
