2002
01:38:22,034 --> 01:38:23,631
What?

2003
01:38:23,633 --> 01:38:26,099
You said that name
when you were asleep.

2004
01:38:26,101 --> 01:38:27,867
You seemed upset.

2005
01:38:28,667 --> 01:38:30,631
Was he your friend who...

2006
01:38:30,633 --> 01:38:31,967
Yeah, I...

2007
01:38:32,767 --> 01:38:34,366
I worked with him, I...

2008
01:38:34,368 --> 01:38:38,265
I worked for him,
but I met him when I was 12.

2009
01:38:38,267 --> 01:38:42,531
I was at that Catholic home
for boys on DeKalb.

2010
01:38:42,533 --> 01:38:44,232
They threw me in there
when I was six,

2011
01:38:44,234 --> 01:38:45,667
after my mother died.

2012
01:38:46,867 --> 01:38:48,765
Frank...

2013
01:38:48,767 --> 01:38:52,633
Frank kind of took me
under his wing.

2014
01:38:55,067 --> 01:38:57,034
You know, he never
called me my name.

2015
01:38:58,468 --> 01:38:59,967
He called me Brooklyn.

2016
01:39:01,201 --> 01:39:03,065
Say, "Look at you,
Motherless Brooklyn,

2017
01:39:03,067 --> 01:39:05,767
you got no one
lookin' out for ya."

