We all need someone
lookin' out for us.

2019
01:39:25,800 --> 01:39:27,533
[water running]

2020
01:39:32,500 --> 01:39:34,565
Is that your mother?

2021
01:39:34,567 --> 01:39:36,732
She's beautiful.

2022
01:39:36,734 --> 01:39:38,934
[Laura] She died
a long time ago.

2023
01:39:40,633 --> 01:39:42,234
I don't remember her.

2024
01:39:44,600 --> 01:39:47,531
I guess we both
got nobody now.

2025
01:39:47,533 --> 01:39:49,598
Listen, I gotta ask you,

2026
01:39:49,600 --> 01:39:51,299
is there something
you're not tellin' me?

2027
01:39:51,301 --> 01:39:52,865
What?

2028
01:39:52,867 --> 01:39:54,332
Is there something you're
holdin' out, you and Horowitz?

2029
01:39:54,334 --> 01:39:55,967
On all this housing deal?

2030
01:39:57,267 --> 01:39:58,531
Look, the...

2031
01:39:58,533 --> 01:39:59,798
Those goons at the BA,

2032
01:39:59,800 --> 01:40:00,999
